title: Episode 299: Ride it Bareback (Feat. Payroll Giovanni & Cardo Got Wings)
itunes:title: Episode 299: Ride it Bareback (Feat. Payroll Giovanni & Cardo Got Wings)
description:
Rapper, Payroll Giovanni and Producer, Cardo Got Wings join the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote their latest project "Another Day Another Dollar." Payroll and Cardo discuss the ups and downs of their 10 year long relationships, dealing with annoying people in the studio, and much more. The ladies almost made Cardo spill the tea regarding Drake AND Kendrick's upcoming albums. Enjoy!


P.S. We apologize for Cardo's bad Wifi connection. Make sure to go tell him to get it fixed in his Instagram comments....tell him we sent you.
